{"tid":1183572,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"港府：4月樓價超97年高位逾倍　密切留意市況","createTime":"2019-06-03T04:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T05:25:41.000Z","uid":221051,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"8e633193cd3066205cd48854b72ac24488edf389","tid":1183572,"uid":221051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波表示，市場對貿易摩擦升溫的憂慮減少，環球股市復甦，加上對美國聯儲局進一步加息預期減退，本港樓市自1月起反彈，首4個月的月均成交量回升至5,400宗，較去年第4季增82%。 <br />\n<br />\n他指出，本港樓價已連升4個月，4月份整體樓價已較去年12月反彈約9%，距去年歷史高位低約1%，而4月樓價仍比1997年高峰高出1.26倍，首季置業供款佔市民收入比重仍高達69%，超出市民負擔能力。 <br />\n<br />\n他稱，未來3至4年一手私人住宅供應量將會達到9.3萬伙，未來5年平均每年落成量達1.88萬伙，較過去5年年均落成量增加約20%，政府未來會密切留意樓市。"},{"pid":"2752eabe4397151dfb8bffe07fb0a0c6823fbaf1","tid":1183572,"uid":18764,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b384664a54368c9c08fd848ffc02567740f50e","tid":1183572,"uid":106756,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"有財爺呢句就放心曬，即係樓價繼續gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b510f3c336a5900968dfa68cb2ccdfdfc5ab0913","tid":1183572,"uid":136833,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"個個月都話會 注意講廢話"},{"pid":"e30ea105e853a97ef19b027d9a09a29597ffcbc1","tid":1183572,"uid":76753,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"乜撚都淨係識講密切留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6314d195845aef51d59cd614ae396e4924a1bd5","tid":1183572,"uid":19676,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e30ea105e853a97ef19b027d9a09a29597ffcbc1","tid":1183572,"uid":76753,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"乜撚都淨係識講密切留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T04:54:01.0